      • enumerate

        public void enumerate(ModularEnumerator enumerator,
                      java.lang.String profile)
        Description copied from interface: EnumeratorModule
        Find loadable mods in this enumerator's domain, the enumerator module should call back against the enumerator itself to register containers it discovers using the registerModContainer() and registerTweakContainer() callbacks. This method is called during loader PREINIT phase so **DO NOT USE ANY GAME CLASSES HERE**!
